IIRC, the Bentley doesn't mention anything about sealant, just install and
torque to 14ftlb (please double-check before taking my word). I've seen
posts elsewhere of folks using a non-curing sealant to avoid leaks, but it's
often pointed out that it is not necessary. Mike


